 OPF_Briefing_1n1_EnemyForces {
  coords 5809.926 272.42 10244.987
  m_sTitle "A. Enemy Forces:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>A. Enemy Forces:</h2>"\
  "<b>Equipment:</b>"\
  "<i>Seperatists are equipped with mismatch of Pact weaponry, AK series, RPG7s, PKMs, RPKs."\
  "Wearing the mismatch of uniforms.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Known Strength:</b>"\
  "<i>1x Rifle Platoon</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Location:</b>"\
  "<i>Holding out at the town of Zarichne</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Capabilities:</b>"\
  "<i>Access to RPGs, PKMs, VOGs, AT Mines."\
  "Vehicles include LAVs provided by the Americans.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>MLCOA:</b>"\
  "<i>Continue to fortify and place down mines, utilizing the urban area to deny our usage of the vehicles.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>MDCOA:</b>"\
  "<i>Mine all the roads, funnel our infantry into kill zones and evading our attempt to pin and destroy them.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Defensive Fires:</b>"\
  "<i>No known in-direct threat at this time.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Airthreat:</b>"\
  "<i>No access to air assets thankfully..</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>Morale:</b>"\
  "<i>Very High.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>CBRN Threat:</b>"\
  "<i>The enemy pose no CBRN Threat as of now.</i>"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 OPF_Briefing_1n2_FriendlyForces {
  coords 5810.485 272.436 10244.991
  m_sTitle "B. Friendly Forces:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>B. Friendly Forces</h2>"\
  "<b>a. Disposition:</b>"\
  "<i>All NVA Forces in the area (YOU) are marked on the map south of Zarichne</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>b. Higher Units Mission:</b>"\
  "<i>Our unit is assigned to secure the town of Zarichne and push the Seperatists out</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>c. Composition:</b>"\
  "<i>1x Rifle Company (-)"\
  "1x T-72A Section.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>d. Strength:</b>"\
  "<i>Company HQ - At 4x Man Strength"\
  "1st Platoon - At 23x Man Strength."\
  "2nd Platoon - At 23x Man Strength."\
  "T-72 Section - 2x Tank Strength, 6x Man Strength.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>e. Supporting Fires:</b>"\
  "<i>Mortar Barrage will commence once we start moving towards Zarichne</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>f. Attachments/Detachments:</b>"\
  "<i>1x T-72 Section</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>g. Additional Ammunition</b>"\
  "<i>Some additional supplies at the UAZs</i>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 OPF_Briefing_2_Mission {
  coords 5810.876 272.451 10244.802
  m_sTitle "II. Mission:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>II: Mission</h2>"\
  "<i>NOTE: Mortar Barrage of Zarichne will commence once you step off towards the town itself."\
  ""\
  "Secure the town of Zarichne from the Seperatists fortified there, destroying the LAV Section and establish your own defences there facing North."\
  ""\
  "We've located Three AT Minefield (Marked on map), however there may be more, Wrenches as needed to clear the path for the T-72As as needed"\
  ""\
  "No Civilians in the area</i>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 OPF_Briefing_3_Execution {
  coords 5811.153 272.461 10244.768
  m_sTitle "III. Execution:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>III: Execution</h2>"\
  "<b>Intent:</b>"\
  "<i>Secure the town of Zarichne and push the Seperatists out!</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>1. Concept of the Operation:</b>"\
  "<i>Company Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is adviced to utilize the T-72s to lock down roads so the Platoons can clear our sections of buildings together, and to prevent the enemy from running across the roads into new buildings or trying to support the locked in units.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>2. Maneuver</b>"\
  "<i>Company Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is adviced to keep the platoons together so they can mutually support one another alongside the T-72s</i>"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 OPF_Briefing_4_Sustainment {
  coords 5811.303 272.534 10244.736
  m_sTitle "IV. Sustainment:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>IV: Sustainment</h2>"\
  "<b>a. SOP Variations</b>"\
  "<i>Dress: Standard NVA Uniform"\
  "Equipment: Standard NVA Loadout</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>b. Logistical Support:</b>"\
  "<i>Replen Plan: None for 24h."\
  "Ammunition: Each man carries his own ammunition."\
  "IPE: Helmets and body armour are to be worn at all times."\
  "No Rearm available for the T-72s</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>c. Medical:</b>"\
  "<i>Location: Company Aid Post is to be setup by company medics."\
  "CASEVAC: By foot or with company asset like the Ambulance."\
  "Plan: Set up a casualty collection point and extract casualties to this point."\
  "Stretchers: None"\
  "Med Packs: Company medpack carried by company medic."\
  "Morphine: Every soldier carries 1+ stick of morphine.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>d. Vehicles:</b>"\
  "<i>2x T-72As"\
  "2x UAZ452s"\
  "1x UAZ452 Ambulance"\
  ""\
  "In each UAZ452:"\
  "4x Bandages"\
  "24x Wrenches</i>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
